{"tid":494014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男子不願3P　狠女咬爆陰莖濺血稱自衛","createTime":"2017-12-09T07:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T09:38:44.000Z","uid":34498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"507a6f4ef969c2250b6ee6a468820d89dc9488aa","tid":494014,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"來自義大利、到英國愛丁堡餐廳工作的43歲女子維希歐(Nunzia Del Viscio)，涉嫌在去年5月咬爆44歲男子帕爾馬(Marcello Palma)的陰莖，該案近日再度開庭審理。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，案情顯示，去年5月23日，維希歐下班後和帕爾馬到酒吧喝酒，當酒吧結束營業後，維希歐與帕爾馬以及另外2名友人，一起到帕爾馬的公寓。然後維希歐以全裸之姿，衝進帕爾馬的房間，並上了帕爾馬的床對他說：「我要3P。」但帕爾馬拒絕，隨後維希歐馬上變身成「咬莖女」，當場狠咬帕爾馬的生殖器，導致帕爾馬濺血，床鋪與地板血跡斑斑。而帕爾馬為了推開維希歐，也朝維希歐的臉部打去，導致維希歐臉上與眼睛黑青。帕爾馬之後被送醫急救，縫了15針，警方也目擊到維希歐滿嘴是血。維希歐向檢警辯稱，自己是出於自衛才咬陰莖，而她也承認有飲酒及嗑藥。最後維希歐被判6個月內的晚間10時到隔日清晨6時這段期間，必須待在家裡，另外還要賠給帕爾馬500英鎊(約新台幣2萬元)賠償金。<br />\n台灣網友紛紛表示：「真的GG了。」、「我我我...看到妳也硬不起來。」、「就算是再民主的國家，也會將惡男惡女的照片公開，以避免他們容易再犯。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n <br />\n帕爾馬不願3P，狠女維希歐咬爆陰莖濺血稱自衛。翻自《太陽報》<br />\n <a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20171209/1256185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20171209%2F1256185&d=0f1PjH4DZh8cit4d2DdfqP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=291b19cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20171209%2F1256185&h=ac504ec1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20171209/1256185</a>[/quote]"},{"pid":"9cb06d2b0ec5764d5c4049120e8f2bf131c932cf","tid":494014,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171209/640_ab467401194c1c9f24072a9d6da66c71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171209%2F640_ab467401194c1c9f24072a9d6da66c71.jpg&h=bcc35063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53d8e4d1015f8f737d9844743c799194eabb381c","tid":494014,"uid":7161,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"你試下係個男人要求3p 之後咬爛條女個閪"},{"pid":"7b39d26d1e5b8190f3d3f6f34500839cc51f60c6","tid":494014,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da578cd3f2c554fc9f95cf5c625161a0be369bc","tid":494014,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bfc57170d4bcb8ece652940ecc0f23bf26a6ed","tid":494014,"uid":49979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你試下係個男人要求3p 之後咬爛條女個閪</blockquote><br />\n女權撚即刻要搞番個全國運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打住女性被拳打面為由大字報洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a6760381f2524c12a32a01ada1524a7a7e8af7","tid":494014,"uid":151512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"比個咁撚樣嘅女人咬爆條撚<br />\n個男人前世殺佢全家？"}]}